{"tid":1489409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國商務部延長華為採購許可90天","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:53:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7643b198eaf896314ca9f2db79e5d75cb84e45f3","tid":1489409,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"美國商務部延長華為採購許可90天<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475586-20190819.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475586-20190819.htm&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex3qIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=b2fa1c48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475586-20190819.htm&h=fce7194b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475586-20190819.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國延長中國電信設備商華為向美國企業購買產品的寬限期90日，但同時將華為的46間子公司，列入威脅美國國家安全的「實體名單」，代表過百間相關公司受限制。<br />\n<br />\n商務部長羅斯在聲明表示，在促請消費者由華為轉用其他產品期間，發現需要更多時間以避免出現混亂。新的寬限期將延遲到今年11月19日。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯表示，華為技術上是私人企業，但於中國法律之下，私人企業都需要與軍方及中國情報機關合作，他們亦要將有關工作保密。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前重申，因為國家安全的原因，不想同華為做生意。"},{"pid":"4a7d8dbe0b4db10e5da1262bda818f1cde937d5e","tid":1489409,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9106c08f664f97f8970abe8e5be298223bc8136","tid":1489409,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695c9161ea7ae83c78f0d63cffd18d927eaf3a66","tid":1489409,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji